Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了，咒术天球被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们胜利啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.15,0:02:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切总算…都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了，我们赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.85,0:02:22.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.94,0:02:35.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么还活着?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色的…月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:14.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是真正的咒术天球…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在艾尔利亚近郊的高能源反应…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是它发出来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,『当通天剑塔贯穿天际之时…\N黑色的月亮将会出现』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是破灭的纹章了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.06,0:03:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说克洛德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在该怎么办哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说啊，克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉库尔希望已经不能发射了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼头，你们不要吵了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼头?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是小鬼头呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.18,0:03:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快回到我的船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这里都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:12.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们马上来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.85,0:04:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家要小心 这是机械军团
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们赶快逃到船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.94,0:04:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:27.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在胡说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.80,0:04:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们怎么可以丢下你们自己跑呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是说这些的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.55,0:04:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们不用担心我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说得对，相信我们就对了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我们  一定会再见的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错，你们快点上船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧?我们要留在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.25,0:04:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.46,0:04:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要去救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧，既然这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.88,0:04:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波曼医生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:04:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不走，我要留在这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.78,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.96,0:05:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.55,0:05:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好，交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:07.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们干什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧佩菈，我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.10,0:05:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是悬崖耶，克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.95,0:06:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你说，看了也知道是悬崖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:21.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定又有什么惊人的想法了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也只有试试了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在要是有对翅膀就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.58,0:06:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有『幸运』的翅膀…那就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:32.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的这句话我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.25,0:06:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们飞吧，阿修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,飞?你该不是说…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个还用问吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:41.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是叫你跳下去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.15,0:06:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,痛死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里昂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有发抖喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不老实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在太空艇坠毁之前紧急迫降
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.45,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坠毁?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吧?考古学教授?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向神祈祷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救命啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:36.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不怕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里昂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个人就是死鸭子嘴硬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.95,0:07:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧?普莉希丝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.02,0:07:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是洋娃娃，痛死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普莉希丝…里昂…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们找个东西抓稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托，叫你抓个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你抓我干什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要降落了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太乱来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道…他们现在怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边有欧佩菈和艾尔尼斯特跟着\N他们不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要担心的应该是我们吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那么多机械怪物在外面晃来晃去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在到底该怎么办呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:45.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真的…还有什么好办法吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:50.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的还有战胜咒术天球的…方法吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.52,0:08:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信我们最后一定会打赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.45,0:09:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有了这样的信念…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一定会成功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.66,0:09:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要相信希望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.05,0:09:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只要一放弃就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是卡尔纳斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才有个女人的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是卡尔纳斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德·C·肯尼少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人叫的是克洛德的名字耶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说…里昂说的是真的喽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:57.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正在行星卫星轨道上通信当中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:10:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔纳斯号在艾克斯贝尔的卫星轨道上?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔纳斯号…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.15,0:10:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么是卫星轨道?克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.56,0:10:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔纳斯号在这儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔纳斯号现在就在上空?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔纳斯，我是克洛德·C·肯尼少尉，听到请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.65,0:10:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是卡尔纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:29.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你待在原地不要移动我们会有进一步指示
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是罗尼基思·J·肯尼提督
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德，听到请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到请回答，克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:40.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德的爸爸?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德，听到请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是罗尼基思·J·肯尼司令官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.56,0:11:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德，听到请回答
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是探测到高能源反应才接近这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到竟然能找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你被传送到这里来了啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找了你好久了，克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.65,0:11:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个行星因为覆盖着一层高能源的屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡尔纳斯号没有办法进行降落
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们准备把你传送到船上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.78,0:11:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也应该回到你所属的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到我…所属的地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.74,0:11:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得先到电波状态稳定的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都非常期待你的归来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能回卡尔纳斯号了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德，你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说话啊，克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.25,0:12:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定…不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.14,0:12:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须完成我应该做的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这里还有事情没有做完
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:33.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里才是我应该待的地方，爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.14,0:12:43.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道你现在所在的处境吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个星球再过不久之后，就要毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是指咒术天球…巨大的陨石对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.85,0:12:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个高能量体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那个高能量体上空\N所出现的黑色物体就是所谓的『安卡』
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.35,0:13:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安卡?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,N56星系现在就有一股强烈的\N宇宙线不断照射在那个安卡上面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.82,0:13:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙线?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.25,0:13:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.75,0:13:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被搜集的高能量…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的就是为了将那个星球上的生命能量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.58,0:13:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部吸收
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸光所有生命的能量?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来…那个星球便会灭亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这…到底是谁的诡计呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.45,0:13:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一确定的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.18,0:13:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不管是用什么样\N的方法都没有办法阻止这种结局了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.65,0:13:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说…克洛德，你还是回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你妄想向那个高能源体挑战的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也只会徒劳无功…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光凭你一个人的力量根本不会有胜算的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你回去吧，克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.85,0:14:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在是…让你该回去自己世界的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.35,0:14:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蕾娜，你在胡说什么啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.45,0:14:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么也这么说?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然蕾娜都觉得这样比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还能说什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不对?阿修顿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.54,0:14:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你，克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你那里得到的勇气，我们不会忘的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊，我们一定会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.06,0:14:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿修顿…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的事交给我们就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有同伴吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.55,0:14:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出色的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.75,0:15:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提督…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是决定留在这个星球上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.78,0:15:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能为了保护同伴而战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然也为了你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.85,0:15:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有我自己的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗也绝对不会白打的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个星球也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸一定能够理解我的决心吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在要结束通信了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请卡尔纳斯号现在尽速离开这个卫星轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛德…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.15,0:16:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.05,0:16:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风…和光…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这个星球还能感到一丝生气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.04,0:16:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火凤破
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在立刻从卫星轨道上脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.58,0:17:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正式脱离卫星轨道回归原本正常航线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎以80%动力加速中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船身没有任何异状
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.65,0:17:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样根本没完没了啊，克洛德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:41.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住我
